# API & Data Rules

- Validate bodies/queries with Zod from `@frs/shared`
- Enforce RBAC in middleware on every protected route
- Use Prisma transactions for report status change + audit log
- Never expose pending/returned report detail to Project Admin
- CSV import/export only for Foundation sync in Phase 1
